profile:
What we do is we offer a flat rate for the very first clean depending on the size and condition of that house . This guarantees that we are able to clean the neglected areas such as trim , baseboards , doors , ect, as well as the day to day cleaning. This ensures that we are able to start off with a full clean and then continue on with basic cleaning as well as picking one neglected area on top of the basic clean .
For example after the first full clean , we would come in and do the basic cleaning as well as light fixtures. Then the following week we would do the basic cleaning and focus on the trim and so on.
services:
Basic cleaning includes:
-Organization upon room cleaning
-Sweeping/ Vacuuming
-Mopping
-Dusting / Surface cleaning
-Full bathroom clean
-Outer appliances ( inner stove , fridge , microwave ect are all part of the neglected areas we include weekly)
- Main windows ( others are provided when we are focusing on windows on top of the basic cleaning .
